description: I decided to go shopping at one of the largest Asian market in Prague. At first, it looked like a stupid idea but then I met a young man looking for a present for his little son. This guy was pretty interesting. He was only 21 and broke up with his girlfriend just recently. One of the reasons was that he found out that he was bicurious. That really caught my attention. The boy had an incredibly cute face and nice lean body, I was definitely going to have fun with him. I thought it would be easy but he was afraid of doing anything intimate with a stranger. No problem, I had plenty of time to get him to know me better. And I had a lot of money to make my offers irresistible. I managed to undress him a little but the market was too crowded – I had to convince him to go to my place…
title: Czech Hunter 379
